{"type":"text","timestamp":1783579748821,"sessionID":"ses_0ba5db601ffenC2RUSQV0CqsZM","part":{"id":"prt_f45a3140c001K0dTE49ic7EKX1","messageID":"msg_f45a2b3220012M3hpUa7KAH9HN","sessionID":"ses_0ba5db601ffenC2RUSQV0CqsZM","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis:\n\n- Record R000079 belongs to department D001 (投资银行部), amount 226.98, status approved, special_approval = 0.\n- D001 annual budget is 230395.17, but cumulative approved reimbursement is 363614.58, which is about 1.58x the budget — well over the 1.0x threshold.\n- Per policy, once cumulative usage reaches 1.0x of the annual budget, no further reimbursement is allowed without special approval; R000079 has no special approval, so it hits the over-budget anomaly.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"anomaly_ids\": [\"over_budget\"],\n  \"record_ids\": [\"R000079\"],\n  \"answer\": \"命中超预算异常。报销记录R000079属于投资银行部(D001),该部门年度预算为230395.17元,但已审批报销累计金额达363614.58元,已达到并超过年度预算额度的1.0倍(约1.58倍)。按预算管理办法,部门费用累计使用达到年度预算1.0倍后原则上不得继续报销,确需超预算支出的须履行专项审批。R000079为已审批记录且special_approval为0,即未经专项审批,因此命中超预算异常。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\"doc_id\": \"08_budget_management.md\", \"clause_no\": \"第三条\"},\n    {\"doc_id\": \"08_budget_management.md\", \"clause_no\": \"第四条\"},\n    {\"doc_id\": \"01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\", \"clause_no\": \"第十三条\"}\n  ]\n}\n```","time":{"start":1783579743244,"end":1783579748813}}}
